The TDC joined RIDE's public event "How can data and AI drive action on sustainable transport?" during London Climate Action Week, presenting TDC's open data infrastructure alongside the Transport Global Intelligence System (TGIS) prototype, WRI India's SHIFT Transport Initiative, and the University of Oxford's Africa Transport Systems Database.
